{"tid":571364,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"要求移除正負評數多而上熱門依個準則！！","createTime":"2018-02-24T14:45:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-26T09:21:58.000Z","uid":5190,"like":232,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4f2593b580158fc449f2b0a9a7dffe6c34e96615","tid":571364,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T14:45:34.000Z","msg":"屌那星 啲垃圾會員開個垃圾post為左上熱門 就搞埋啲無閪用嘅投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得你公投無所謂 有競爭成份是好的<br />\n<br />\n但啲垃圾 下下到知道個正負皮一定一面倒 都仲要搞啲無意義嘅投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n例如講條女比綠帽條仔 個post就講到條女幾咁仆街幾咁閪 然後最後個無撚用投票就會係<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 條女正臭閪 快啲post佢相<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 分左手就放過人啦 <br />\n<br />\n屌你老母 咁樣又有得投呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咪又係想正皮多 頂個post上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n強烈要求正皮或負皮多嘅因素 唔列入熱門post準則<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不如我為左依個post 又發起個完全無意義嘅投票先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正皮 連登小學生討論區<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  負皮 連登好高質"},{"pid":"e23ea585aaf49f99fa2771366654cb61003f2b75","tid":571364,"uid":5190,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T14:48:52.000Z","msg":"我認我唔清楚上熱門有啲咩要求 但如果你話人流查看個post都係一個上熱門嘅因素 我想問下 10:47分 以下依個post連100個留言都無 但因為正皮而呃左啲人入去 咁樣係咪叫呃人流？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/570989/page/4?ref=ios\" t